			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">虚界护罩：<span color="#9999ff">200虚界</span><span>盾，元素+1，夜魂+3，小龙+80，击破瘫痪黄金王兽24s并且扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">35%</span><span>生命值。<br/>瘫痪时</span><span color="#ffe599">岩抗</span><span>-45%。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
