		<RichText x="739" y="223" width="421" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽蓄力向地面冲去，从场地外向内进行3次撞击，碰到造成<span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽蓄力，贴近地面喷吐渊之岩，接触持续造成<span color="#ffe599">50%,12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害，来回两次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="735" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽，朝空中连续吐出大量「黄金犬首」向玩家处洒落，每个犬首造成<span color="#ffe599">25%,12.5%,6.25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="433" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兽境类原魔造成的伤害都会附带「侵蚀」效果。黄金王兽的效果为：每层每秒扣除玩家<span color="#ffe599">(1%HP+25)</span><span>的生命值，每层持续</span><span color="#ffe599">9.5s</span><span>，持续时间独立计算，可叠加。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="435" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽原地开始旋转蓄力，形成巨大的龙卷风，附属<span textDecoration="underline">虚界护罩</span><span>，蓄力结束时对全场造成</span><span color="#ffe599">500%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>；不过小龙在场的话，它会尽力避免这一刻到来。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
