		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽飞到高空，高速下落坠入地面造成巨大范围的<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害，片刻后钻出，造成</span><span color="#ceffbf">无侵蚀</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffe599">25%</span><span>伤害，随后在场地内产生9个小岩喷造成</span><span color="#ffe599">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="223" width="420" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黄金王兽升空，在空中悬停一会后使用尾部连续扫击两次，均造成<span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
